  "texts": [
    "For the GQS, the average score of each answer was collected, and an overall average score was then calculated.",
    "In all cases, p < 0.05 was considered statistically significant.",
    "ResultsOverall, a total agreement between specialists, in terms of surgical choices, was reached in 60 cases (40 in the \"ordinary\" and 20 in the \"challenging\" subgroups.",
    "Glaucoma phenotypes of the studied cases are summarized in Table 2.Overall, when repeated questions were inserted three times in chatbots' interfaces, ChatGPT gave consistent results in 75% of cases (n = 57).",
    "In 18% of cases, the answers were consistent in 2 out of the 3 repetitions, while on the other side, repeating the question to Google Gemini led to a 72% rate of inconsistency."
